randomartassignment.expression

Class ExpressionParallel

  • java.lang.Object
    • randomartassignment.expression.ExpressionParallel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExpressionParallel.Average, ExpressionParallel.Cos, ExpressionParallel.Multiply, ExpressionParallel.Sin, ExpressionParallel.Variable

    public abstract class ExpressionParallel
extends java.lang.Object
    ExpressionParallel represents a mathematical "expression," by which is meant either a representation of a variable, a mathematical operator, or a mathematical function (such as those of trigonometry). It has been designed to work in a parallel fashion. Subclass this class in order to define more specific types of each.
    Version:
    1.0 20 July 2012
    Author:
    Amndeep Singh Mann
